  <bioghist id="aspace_c291bf6d4d5f7beaba3ec8261ea0def5">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Emily Boardman, of Trumansburg, New York, was a sister of Douglass Boardman, an Ithaca, New York lawyer.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_cb75f2a36dbdcdad82b816bb97ba8a17">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Will, accounts, receipts, and correspondence of Emily Boardman, addressed to George R. Williams pertaining to the settlement of her estate.</p>  </scopecontent>
